702184f-a.folder: Williamsbridge Road & Van Nest Avenue, Bronx, NY
702184f-a.original_title: Bronx: Williamsbridge Road - Van Nest Avenue
702184f-a.text:
Williamsbridge Road, adjoining the N.E. corner of Van Nest Ave., showing the real estate office of Barney Howard. The empty lot (left) adjoins the cottage on the north.
August 3, 1928
P. L. Sperr.
